title: Person of Interest: Reese VS Drug Dealers (III)
author: POI Fights
comment: Every time I stumble across videos of Person Of Interest it becomes REESE TIME. I like Finch too, do not misunderstand, but he does not get physical nor does he want to deal with guns.
He must have late stag rabies if he is scared of water. 🤣
Which would have hurt worse: a faceful of hydrochloric acid, or a double knee-capping?  I'd hate to have to choose...
description: Fight Scene from S01 X 17: Identity Crisis
